Package: sparseEigen
Title: Computation of sparse eigenvectors of a matrix
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Konstantinos Benidis <benidisk@gmail.com> [aut, cre],
    Daniel P. Palomar <daniel.p.palomar@gmail.com> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Konstantinos Benidis <benidisk@gmail.com> [aut, cre],
    Daniel P. Palomar <daniel.p.palomar@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions to compute sparse eigenvectors 
    (while keeping their orthogonality) or sparse PCA from either the 
    covariance matrix or directly the data matrix.
URL: https://github.com/dppalomar/sparseEigen
BugReports: https://github.com/dppalomar/sparseEigen/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
